<h3 id="卷积">卷积</h3>

<p>$f(t)*h(t)=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}f(\tao)h(t-\tao)d\tao$</p>

<h4 id="卷积定理">卷积定理</h4>

<p>$f(t)<em>h(t) \iff F(\mu)H(\mu)$
且
$f(t)h(t) \iff F(\mu)</em>H(\mu)$</p>
